game.name: T Rex NY Online
game.description:
Oh no! The dangerous dinosaur is back with more power and strength! Would you be able to control him to destroy all in his way? If yes, join T Rex NY and be prepared to become the part of the biggest rampage throughout the city. When you click the play button, you would see a ferocious robot T-Rex who is ready to cause the destruction on the streets of your beautiful city New York. Your job is to guide this dinosaur to cause as much destruction and damage as possible in this brand new adventure game.

No need to show pity on the humans as you also have to help this gigantic-sized dinosaur to eat people, wreak havoc and smash vehicles that you see on the road. Try not to let anyone stand in your way and snatch them up before they make any damage to you in this action-packed challenge! Remember this is not a regular dinosaur, but a one created with the help of machinery. Get rid of as many people/objects as you can to collect a significant sum of money!

Hey! The best part is that you can use that money to purchase more upgrades like armour, helmets or new weapons. Your dinosaur is very hungry and you do not have any choice instead of eating humans so do not let the hungriness make a pressure on him. Try to enter like a champion to rack up as many points as possible in this super fun-loving and addictive dinosaur game that is available on atmegame.com for free to play, no download required!
